Package com.versant.odmg

Interface Summary
Bag ODMG 2.0 Java Binding defines the Interface Bag.
Collection ODMG 2.0 Java binding defines the Collection Interface.
List A List object is an ordered collection of persistent objects.
Set A Set object is an unordered collection of elements that does not allow duplicates.
 

Class Summary
Database This class is the ODMG 2.0 compliant Database class.
ODMGSession The ODMGSession class is a wrapper class for an underlying VERSANT session object.
Transaction The predefined type Transaction represents a transaction.
